STACK vs HEAP VISUALIZATION:
1. [Stack] userVar -> [Heap Address: 0x001]
2. [Heap Address: 0x001] -> { name: 'Alice', data: 0x002 }
3. [Heap Address: 0x002] -> { bio: 'Dev' }

When you do `const user2 = userVar`, you create a new entry in the STACK pointing to the same 0x001 address in the HEAP. This is 'Reference Sharing'.
